    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/414e4b273b51b2051987ace2358ba64a.webp?t=1717309545\" width=620 height=56 /></span><br>在这个化为灰烬的世界里，只有昏暗的交通信号灯静静地标记着时间。<br>仅存的几个人的身体被烧成灰烬，他们正在进入最后的时光。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/1c17b96609b5a2ebdac64b0753fc6bc2.poster.avif?t=1717309545\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/1c17b96609b5a2ebdac64b0753fc6bc2.webm?t=1717309545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/1c17b96609b5a2ebdac64b0753fc6bc2.mp4?t=1717309545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>但与一个被丢弃的腐烂玩偶的相遇却改变了你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/52ca577655da4559b02b7be34320f948.poster.avif?t=1717309545\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/52ca577655da4559b02b7be34320f948.webm?t=1717309545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/52ca577655da4559b02b7be34320f948.mp4?t=1717309545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/2cc5c18f5de3e9205f25daaa1a3fc7b3.webp?t=1717309545\" width=620 height=56 /></span><br>您可以用灯笼和火柴的光烧掉覆盖城市的灰烬。<br>通过消除城市中的污染，您将逐步扩大自己的行动范围。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/940af17dadb39247bc0ba6a9a44f8329.poster.avif?t=1717309545\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/940af17dadb39247bc0ba6a9a44f8329.webm?t=1717309545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/940af17dadb39247bc0ba6a9a44f8329.mp4?t=1717309545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>它的光芒甚至可以烧死被污染的生物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/2f3cb136841250b39969283cb42a919e.webp?t=1717309545\" width=620 height=56 /></span><br>城市里一定还有微弱的食物供应来维持生命。<br>在垃圾箱中寻找，在肮脏的地方搜刮，生存下去。<br><br>可用的旧货币还可以用来从自动售货机上获得各种物品。<br>增强自己的体质，在基地里安装起码的家具，会让你的日子过得更好一些。<br><br>有了充足的储备，你就会有更大的行动空间。<br>随着更多的污染被清除，你的生活得到改善，你和你的娃娃们一定会感觉更好。<br>但是，随着光线越来越强，黑暗也会随之而来...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/0d7a0ce5082266d65b6c7529f3336428.poster.avif?t=1717309545\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/0d7a0ce5082266d65b6c7529f3336428.webm?t=1717309545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007200/extras/0d7a0ce5082266d65b6c7529f3336428.mp4?t=1717309545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>( Teaser Movie BGM by Hashimami )",
